{"tid":2499412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港騙徒手法整合post，睇完唔好再中招","createTime":"2021-04-22T01:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T02:59:19.000Z","uid":74908,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"882f25b4aa43990d004c342d0f6b169197e65f49","tid":2499412,"uid":74908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:00:08.000Z","msg":"騙徒手法層出不窮，香港人太多天真好心人<br />\n每隔段時間就有受害人年經月經post講自己被人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上得兩登多嘅人都知道係邊款騙徒<br />\n但都有唔少人未見過<br />\n希望一齊整理一份騙徒list方便了解騙徒生態<br />\n唔好再被呃啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049c8c579213b2cd50cbf08719629e3139f5a1de","tid":2499412,"uid":74908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:15:42.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><ins><span class=\"red\">不幸外國人</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n手法：聲稱非常不幸被人偷/跌銀包，冇晒錢可唔可以幫幫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時會周圍去求路人做好心<br />\n坐低路邊，只靠一塊紙皮黑色箱頭筆寫住自己「不幸」經歷都見過<br />\n<br />\n外貌：鬼佬，backpacker裝扮多<br />\n<br />\n出現地點：樓主佐敦，尖沙咀同旺角都見過<br />\n應該遊客區多<br />\n<br />\n單人/團隊：單人出現，私底下應該團隊運作<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSSJbcce9nnhU8f9iuNHRbZjCcYb2CVhuvQciforCQRd9?filename=j5y7PNf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj5y7PNf.jpg&h=1070ad4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aee5ca2a6a7b304c98a2b366e664e6f4a61714e0","tid":2499412,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:24:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e851192a045433203956dcf4b5b7b84eba31dd9","tid":2499412,"uid":335883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:25:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23cb64e05a892c0f00676101f942c06fe174147d","tid":2499412,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:30:57.000Z","msg":"<ins>林鄭月娥</ins><br />\n叫人上大灣區投資，市民出事俾人呃走投無路投訴無門<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b175382ccef1898e9719ba085c8568ec1787ea","tid":2499412,"uid":74908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T01:44:21.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><ins><span class=\"red\">是日本人Eddie</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n手法：職業千變萬化嘅「日本人」，但又會有英文名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身份呢次係大學教授下次可以係designer<br />\n一開始會問點搭去機場，之後就會好緊張講呢個方法唔夠時間去機場點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得返飛的一個方法但幾百蚊車費身上唔夠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n引受害者借錢後，會好有報恩心<br />\n留各種聯絡方式例如電話號碼 whatsapp,email等等<br />\n聲稱一定會還ali加多<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外貌：樓主未見過，但見有人影低過<br />\n<br />\n出現地點：遊客區<br />\n<br />\n單人/團隊：Eddie咁出名全港得你一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUc5jrbqktNDYjJHR4fNeNZoDpSYi7ysYaghMXVJoFcek?filename=pQhsPV8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpQhsPV8.jpg&h=cc273111&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e84b7b1162f97f44a65b0fcfe5d1f550bb5dbbc2","tid":2499412,"uid":258758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279f9a75c949a58464bedda897568f997e355d1d","tid":2499412,"uid":74908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:39:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\"><ins>假聾啞人</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n手法：扮聾啞人士，識手語可以撚返佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手持小朋友都唔要嘅垃圾玩具/公仔/筆記簿仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n周圍向人以極度唔合理價格兜售，身上掛住一個證件套show俾人睇<br />\n「我係聾啞人士，請好心支持xx協會blablabla」<br />\n每件垃圾貨物都有價錢牌，派傳單咁強行塞俾人<br />\n唔願意買或者唔夠錢，就會惡死捉住人強迫要買/出夠錢，而且不設找續<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應付方法：要夠惡過對方千祈唔可以要<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外貌：衣着單易樸素，部分個樣似弱智人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出現地點：各區都有<br />\n<br />\n單人/團隊：多數2,3位出現，有人會扮義工輔助<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdLLYTfHeybPbEZW3rpX3Cdd35dut6ywteQffoDLoGRqb?filename=yiD0qOO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyiD0qOO.jpg&h=6bf31dc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPv8qfu2mLTBnjgsUY9pncvhtJdetWk3ZZiRgUF6Nv7jS?filename=eVvJ719.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeVvJ719.png&h=5f45d5d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1640dbe2ba88f3a1ea36b32eb3b95bc5704bb00c","tid":2499412,"uid":74908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:43:55.000Z","msg":"有冇人接手可以講講大規模嘅層壓式推銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登最多人中都係呢樣"},{"pid":"7f7f1b769f6c88d9397838bc5b18a231d6f818f5","tid":2499412,"uid":100985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:54:17.000Z","msg":"樓主圖文講解幾有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，幫推"},{"pid":"416d1b93087a0ffca563207a37b43554e96baee7","tid":2499412,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:54:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反疫苗撚<br />\n叫人唔好打敗康tec<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己衝去打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bec1da7c033ca16a92a3e9632f6fb40a32639e1","tid":2499412,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bus.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}